sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>8444/TCP Health
    participant OAuth as OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Backend as Dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS
    participant MRUI as Model Registry UI<br/>8043/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,K8s: Flow 1: User Authentication and Dashboard Access

    User->>Router: GET / (HTTPS/443)<br/>Initial request
    Router->>Proxy: Forward to 8443/TCP<br/>TLS Reencrypt
    Proxy->>OAuth: OAuth redirect<br/>No valid token
    OAuth->>User: Login prompt
    User->>OAuth: User credentials<br/>HTTPS/443
    OAuth->>User: OAuth Bearer Token<br/>Redirect to dashboard
    User->>Proxy: GET / with Bearer Token<br/>HTTPS/8443
    Proxy->>K8s: TokenReview API<br/>Validate token<br/>HTTPS/443
    K8s-->>Proxy: Token valid + user identity
    Proxy->>Backend: HTTP/8080<br/>X-Auth-Request-User header<br/>(impersonation)
    Backend-->>Proxy: Dashboard HTML/JS
    Proxy-->>User: HTTPS/8443<br/>Dashboard UI

    Note over User,K8s: Flow 2: Notebook Creation

    User->>Proxy: POST /api/notebooks<br/>HTTPS/8443<br/>Bearer Token + JSON payload
    Proxy->>Backend: HTTP/8080<br/>Impersonation headers
    Backend->>K8s: POST /apis/kubeflow.org/v1/namespaces/{ns}/notebooks<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>ServiceAccount + Impersonation
    K8s-->>Backend: Notebook CR created<br/>Resource spec
    Backend-->>Proxy: HTTP/8080<br/>Success response
    Proxy-->>User: HTTPS/8443<br/>Notebook details (JSON)

    Note over User,Prom: Flow 3: WebSocket Resource Watch

    User->>Proxy: WebSocket Upgrade<br/>wss://dashboard/wss/k8s/namespaces/{ns}/notebooks<br/>Bearer Token
    Proxy->>Backend: ws://localhost:8080/wss/k8s/...<br/>Impersonation headers
    Backend->>K8s: WebSocket Watch API<br/>wss://k8s-api:443/apis/kubeflow.org/.../notebooks?watch=true<br/>ServiceAccount + Impersonation
    K8s-->>Backend: Stream: ADDED/MODIFIED/DELETED events
    Backend-->>Proxy: Stream: Resource updates
    Proxy-->>User: Stream: Real-time updates<br/>wss://dashboard:8443

    Note over User,MRUI: Flow 4: Model Registry UI Access (Modular Architecture)

    User->>Proxy: GET /model-registry/*<br/>HTTPS/8443<br/>Bearer Token
    Proxy->>Backend: HTTP/8080<br/>Module federation proxy
    Backend->>MRUI: HTTPS/8043<br/>x-forwarded-access-token: {Bearer Token}
    MRUI->>K8s: Model Registry Backend API<br/>User token from header
    K8s-->>MRUI: Model metadata
    MRUI-->>Backend: HTML/JS/JSON
    Backend-->>Proxy: HTTP/8080
    Proxy-->>User: HTTPS/8443<br/>Model Registry UI

    Note over User,Prom: Flow 5: Prometheus Metrics Query

    User->>Proxy: POST /api/prometheus<br/>HTTPS/8443<br/>Bearer Token + PromQL query
    Proxy->>Backend: HTTP/8080<br/>Impersonation headers
    Backend->>Prom: POST /api/v1/query<br/>HTTPS/9091<br/>ServiceAccount Token + PromQL
    Prom-->>Backend: HTTPS/9091<br/>Metrics data (JSON)
    Backend-->>Proxy: HTTP/8080<br/>Formatted metrics
    Proxy-->>User: HTTPS/8443<br/>Metrics visualization data
